title: Canberra .NET User Group - February
sessionTitle: ​No Estimates - Stop lying to your yourself and your customers, and stop estimating
eventShortDescription:
​No Estimates - Stop lying to your yourself and your customers, and stop estimating

Gerard Beckerleg will take a dive into the depths of this controversial topic and extract the most interesting ideas and raise some very difficult questions about the big white elephant in the room that is Software Estimation.
